{"tid":1370771,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"突發：中共恐嚇獨立調查委員！","createTime":"2019-07-27T05:49:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T05:56:25.000Z","uid":260988,"like":12,"dislike":60,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"bae0d44138178aa79cc8e876e1c8e311c73c4181","tid":1370771,"uid":260988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T05:49:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">抱歉標題黨<br />\n<br />\n有好多人一廂情願獨立調查委員會，能公正調查<br />\n<br />\n香港司法夠獨立啦掛，暗角七警咪又係放生兩個<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CPb9Rf7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCPb9Rf7.png&h=96af2aac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n成個政制崩壞，要有幾壞有幾壞，要有幾勾結有幾勾結，為上者個個自保，遮住良心講大話<br />\n<br />\n中共有冇落指令？有冇參與？獨立調查委員會，夠唔夠膽指正中共？會唔會洩露囯家机密？<br />\n<br />\n委員敢指證中共嘅話，有咩下場？<br />\n<br />\n一個腐爛制度搞出嚟嘅委員會，比佢拖一年半載，出一個爛鬼廢話報告，你覺得機會大唔大呢？</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">制度已經不可信，委員會會出廢報告：正評</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">我信政府，我信制度，我信中共唔搞鳩委員會：負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"1c3a4ad27a5ab6d76b4e62cfdc48323c0324d8ce","tid":1370771,"uid":260988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T05:49:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f1d6aa9e2696268f739bfbf12a168e340552fb0f","tid":1370771,"uid":260988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T05:49:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"efdec285da93b6ff044445a20c0687f645816171","tid":1370771,"uid":260988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T05:49:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6ca4e1cf36a70d4608804200553696cd6cee3a6a","tid":1370771,"uid":260988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T05:50:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f78f65a74871ee1d0d891eb74ad093043cb9f3dd","tid":1370771,"uid":4931,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T05:50:51.000Z","msg":"任何標題黨都請收下負評，內文唔會睇及終止討論。<br />\n<br />\n完"},{"pid":"8a908a36b977bda3689d0e4fad1563e19786c760","tid":1370771,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T05:50:58.000Z","msg":"唔好再回，集中今日活動<br />\n懷疑今日用哩樣引戰洗版<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【緊急！置頂！】三毛最新風向：反對成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1370130\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1370130</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4d5a504f23a6220cc89dd1a33c376df2c545410a","tid":1370771,"uid":264369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T05:51:05.000Z","msg":"BLOCK"},{"pid":"6da9e9de59adea837f32e4bb1e9e5e97e604cc0a","tid":1370771,"uid":235374,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T05:51:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一日冇雙普選<br />\n就算有獨立調查委員會<br />\n不要給予政府任何合法性<br />\n任何特首都只係傀儡</span></span>"},{"pid":"0e9668f4ea77830294a9342fb63605376062270c","tid":1370771,"uid":140326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T05:51:15.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">三毛！負評上一頁</span></span></strong><br />\n【緊急！置頂！】三毛最新風向：反對成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1370130\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1370130</a>"},{"pid":"ad946fe07f331967c0b07d59038c2564252f72e2","tid":1370771,"uid":260988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T05:51:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7c8257f51dc1744caa69d5607da3d40a049309c8","tid":1370771,"uid":149844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T05:51:23.000Z","msg":"坐過監仲有無得做警犬"},{"pid":"2872e090e7169880b69e313f96c5b417473204d8","tid":1370771,"uid":260988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e9668f4ea77830294a9342fb63605376062270c","tid":1370771,"uid":140326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T05:51:15.000Z","msg":"<strong><s